g/zh-hk/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2599&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td6NFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=a002bff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%99</a><br />\n<br />\n我估你係講呢個。我細個有學過，的確對學英文好有幫助，但果時學校唔會教（而家唔知），淨係話你知點讀，無教個發音原理，死記；學識左個發音原理之後，就算見到唔識既字都識讀出來。<br />\n<br />\n不過你喺外國，洗乜學呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵啲鬼傾多啲計，唔好怕人地介意"},{"pid":"b1645bb46dbbfd5ed30074218bd63cff19a9358b","tid":1040607,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"學一個新語言最好既方法就係同當地人一齊生活，係最有效既做法；你有咁既機會唔好浪費。如果你係連開口都有困難果種，政府應該有啲課程俾外來人口學語言"},{"pid":"83b525df5b5e9ee0fa05d9806038e0baa2037051","tid":1040607,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fc5204a16402d822f2602674d171026943a27d","tid":1040607,"uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c07a8c10c4baf2fe07a76e660f6bc619a4c393d1","tid":1040607,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"697373f22b7b275865bab503c4f8df0a9e8797b1","tid":1040607,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"你指phonetic symbol?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"唔識分，係想學個啲，望住唔識嘅字，但係拼到讀音個種，同聽完識拼返出嚟個種。啱先過咗外國冇幾耐，好多嘢都唔識仲摸索緊。英文好差"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2599&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td6NFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=a002bff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%99</a><br />\n<br />\n我估你係講呢個。我細個有學過，的確對學英文好有幫助，但果時學校唔會教（而家唔知），淨係話你知點讀，無教個發音原理，死記；學識左個發音原理之後，就算見到唔識既字都識讀出來。<br />\n<br />\n不過你喺外國，洗乜學呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵啲鬼傾多啲計，唔好怕人地介意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a54f48da96047593bf5e36e205bd4bbacb76011","tid":1040607,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"上YouTube 搵套phonics 跟住學<br />\n學左a-z 發音就再blending <br />\n上網有好多兒歌跟住唱又得<br />\n一路做動作一路唱歌記又得(Jolly Phonics)"},{"pid":"a4edc5fe51d98886fedd9c472c4734d54a51006e","tid":1040607,"uid":4686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"英文係irregular phonetic pattern <br />\nE.g.<br />\nThough<br />\nThrough<br />\nTough<br />\nThorough <br />\n<br />\nSimilar Spelling =/= similar pronunciation<br />\n<br />\n學英文拼音是廢的 just a pedagogical marketing strategy"},{"pid":"f50b829ad83f358384acfeb81025bb03801ccd10","tid":1040607,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:17:17.000Z","msg":"老土講<br />\n其實好學點睇下報紙新聞<br />\n睇下有字幕既戲<br />\n成日見既字就查下點解 點讀<br />\n已經夠你日常工作生活9成8用途 識講識用<br />\n<br />\n反而學識文法/句字 會實用好多好多"},{"pid":"0685037cbf4ece75079d94e429d43fb79bcd5082","tid":1040607,"uid":238541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"認真，無乜用"},{"pid":"c766b34124b9583f9db2a4ae32720bab0bf5ebbb","tid":1040607,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}